==Event Tasks==
*After maintenance, {{Elite}} '''[[Little Renown]]''' {{BC}} will provisionally join your fleet after you log into the game.
*You can collect '''Trust''' by clearing normal mode story maps or [[Crimson Echoes Rerun]] event maps during the event.
*By accumulating '''Trust''', you can clear limited event missions and obtain rewards such as gold and items.
*'''[[Little Renown]]''' will permanently join your fleet after you clear the last mission.
